---
import AIAnswerMockup from './AIAnswerMockup.astro';
---

<section class="bg-surface py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <!-- Copy -->
      <div>
        <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-md bg-yellow-brand px-3 py-1 text-sm font-bold text-navy">The future of search</span>
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold leading-tight text-navy md:text-[40px]">Search is changing. Are you showing up in AI answers?</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>Millions of people now ask AI tools — ChatGPT, Google's AI Overviews, Perplexity — questions like "who are the best roofers in Atlanta" or "how much does HVAC replacement cost." These AI tools pull from the web and decide whose business to mention.</p>
          <p>Most contractors aren't being cited. Not because they're bad at their job — because their content isn't structured for AI to read and trust.</p>
          <p>Happy House builds AEO and GEO into every content piece we produce. That means structured Q&A content, authoritative entity signals, and citation-ready formatting. Your business gets mentioned in AI answers while your competitors haven't even heard of the problem yet.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/how-it-works#aeo" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-lg border-2 border-sky-brand px-6 py-3 font-bold text-sky-brand transition hover:bg-sky-brand/10">Learn how it works &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- AI Mockup -->
      <div class="lg:pl-8">
        <AIAnswerMockup />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
